<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Pocket_stereoscope.jpg" class="image" title="Pocket stereoscope with original test image. Used by military to examine stereoscopic pairs of vertical aerial photographs."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/31/Pocket_stereoscope.jpg/250px-Pocket_stereoscope.jpg" width="250" height="176" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Pocket_stereoscope.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
