</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:XEyeStCdNYCSmall.jpg" class="image" title="Stereo card image modified for crossed eye viewing.View of Manhattan, c. 1909"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3d/XEyeStCdNYCSmall.jpg/250px-XEyeStCdNYCSmall.jpg" width="250" height="126" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:XEyeStCdNYCSmall.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
